<!-- Demonstration of how it works -->
<div class="container">
<div id="last">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="  col-sm-12 center">
      <h1>How it works - A step by step explanation </h1>
     </div>
 </div>
    
    <div class="stepbox">
    <div class="row">
      <div class= "col-sm-12">
        <h3>Step 1</h3> <p class="center steps">Fill the reserve cards with the cards of your choice</p><br/><br/>
    </div>
</div>
    <div class="row">
    
        <div class=" col-sm-6">
       <%= image_tag('reserve_pile1.png', class: ' img-responsive') %> 
    </div>
       <div class=" col-sm-6">
        <%= image_tag('reserse_pile2.png', class: ' img-responsive') %> 
       </div><br/><br/><br/>
  </div>
</div>

   
    <div class="row">
       <div class="stepbox" >
      <div class=" col-sm-12">
        <br/><br/>
        <h3>Step 2</h3><p class="center steps"> Go to the practice pile. The first 5 cards you put in the reserve pile will automatically go to the practice pile. Click on each card to see the other side, trying to memorize its content or to quiz yourself if you think you know it</p><br/><br/>
       </div>
      <div class=" col-sm-12">
         <%= image_tag('pp3.png', class: ' img-responsive') %> 
          <br/><br/>
      </div>
    </div>
      <div class=" col-sm-12">
        <br/><br/>

        <div class="stepbox">
        <h3>Step 3</h3> <p class="center steps">Save each practice by clicking on the red "save practice" button </p>
      <div class="col-sm-12">
         <%= image_tag('pp4.png', class: ' img-responsive') %> 
          <br/><br/>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stepbox">
      <div class=" col-sm-12">

        <br/>
      <h3>Step 4</h3> <p class="center steps">Repeat this process for 15 times, spacing the practice times. <strong>Important note</strong>: during the first 15 viewing of the pile, it will stay unchanged. After that initial period, the pile will <strong>always</strong> be updated after the third viewing of that pile.  
        (the pile stays the same that long at first to allow the first card to leave the pile to have been viewed 15 times, which is the minimum of views necessary for a card leave the pile)</p>
         <br/><br/>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
    <div class=" col-sm-12">
      <br/><br/>
        <h3>After the 15th times you view the pile,  the regular flow of cards starts</h3>
        <p class="center steps">After that, each time  you  view a pile <strong>three</strong> times, it will be updated: the top card will be removed, and another card will be added to the bottom of the pile. And the process will  get repeated, as long as there are cards in the reserve pile.<br/> <br/>
    
        
</div>
</div>
<div class="clearfix hidden-md hidden-lg"></div>

</div>
</div>


    
